intrebare?: What is the role of Search Engine Optimization (SEO)?
raspuns1: Optimizing a search engine to faster generate a result page.
raspuns2: Improving organic traffic to a webpage/website.
raspuns3: Displaying paid advertising in the top 5 positions of a SERP.
raspuns4: Reduce the loading time of a page/site when a user accesses it.
raspuns corect: Improving organic traffic to a webpage/website.
